<body>
	
<header>
	
		
		Now you can watch Dimitris answering the same topic as Alexandra. He started by writing notes. What does Dimitris do during this part of the interview?
		
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <video src="../media/Unit06_e5b.flv" mode="1" id="1002"/>
  <img class="leftFloat" src="../media/MM_SP_004.jpg" mode="1" id="1004"/>
  <p align="left">&#xA0;<g id="t1">A. He follows the instructions on the card.</g></p>
  <p align="left">
    <g id="t2">B. He explains what the advertisement showed.</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <g id="t3">C. He says who it was aimed at.</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <g id="t4">D. He explains what effect it had on him.</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <g id="t5">E. He explains why he finds this type of advert admirable.</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <g id="t6">F. He goes on until the examiner stops him.</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb1">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">A. He should have followed the instructions on the card, but he didn't.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">B. Yes, he explains what the advertisement showed.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">C. He didn't mention this aspect of the advertisement.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">D. Yes, he explains the effect it had on him.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">E. He says he likes it, but not why he finds it admirable.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb6">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#0000ff">F. Always make sure you have answered all the questions before stopping.</font>
  </p>
</section>

